.SH 2. STRING SCANNING
.SH

.SS
var v1 = var().seq();
.nf
‚ÄÖ
.fi
Get the char number of a char

\fBReturns:\fR A number between 0 and 255.

If given a string, then only the first char is considered.

\fBExample:\fR
.RS
