.fi
.RE


.SS
var v1 = conn.loglasterror(source = "");
.nf
‚ÄÖ
.fi
Log the last os or db error message.

\fBOutput:\fR to stdlog

Prefixes the output with source if provided.

\fBExample:\fR
.RS
.nf
 var().loglasterror("main:");
 // or
 loglasterror("main:");
.fi
.RE


